Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.35,0:00:18.32,Lucy-Song-Title,,0,0,0,,[I want to be a rainbow]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:29.78,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa hoshifuru yoru ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:36.71,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono tomoshibi wo keshi wa shinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:47.84,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa akane no asa ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:56.77,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wakaba ni somaru haru wo yobou to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.05,0:01:08.66,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.94,0:01:20.55,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.83,0:01:26.39,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono oosora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:36.19,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:29.78,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow I made on that starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:36.71,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:47.84,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:56.77,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.05,0:01:08.66,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.94,0:01:20.55,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.83,0:01:26.39,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:36.19,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:48.78,Lucy-Ep-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,306.667)\fade(270,470)}Ep. 49 - Clara's Wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:19.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm not sure\Nif I can muster enough courage to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:23.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't feel shy and say it, whatever it may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:26.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If so, let me put it bluntly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:31.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Would you let us adopt Lucy as our daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:35.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Adopt her, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:36.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:38.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural that you're surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:43.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that you'll need to consult\Nwith your wife on a matter like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:46.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But we'd really like to bring Lucy up\Nas if she was our own child.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:51.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If possible, we want to adopt Lucy, by all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:55.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I also share\Na great deal of adoration for Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:59.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it was my wife Sylvia who came to love Lucy\Ndeeply and hopelessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:01.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think I told you about this before,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:04.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,but several years ago we had a daughter,\Nwho had passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:07.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, we were never blessed with a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:12.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, a few days ago, Lucy who had lost her memory\Ncame to stay in our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:17.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My wife started calling Lucy, who couldn't even\Nremember her own name, Emily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:20.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Emily was the name of our late daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:26.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In the time of Lucy's sojourn in our house,\Ndespite me advising her against it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:29.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,my wife came to dote on her,\Nas though she was our own child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:34.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And then, after Lucy's departure,\Nshe feels like a part of her soul had been taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As if we lost our child once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:42.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She only came to realize it keenly after Lucy left us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:44.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Children are a truly wonderful gift from heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:50.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's what my life finally confessed to me today,\Nwho had since became infirm, as if she was actually ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.34,0:03:52.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She was wondering if there's a way\Nwe could adopt Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:56.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, I came to wonder the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:04:00.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If your adorable Lucy becomes our daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:03.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I understand very well how you feel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:05.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, just a moment more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:08.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me say just a couple words more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:13.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, if you happen to agree to us adopting Lucy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:18.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I ought to give you something in exchange,\Nso I'd like to offer you the land in my possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:20.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The land?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:21.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:25.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon my curiosity,\Nbut the thing you currently covet the most -
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:28.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,isn't it a piece of land that you'd own yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:29.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A land?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:33.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you still wish to work on the farm near Gawler,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:37.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I was considering transferring a portion of it\Nto your possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:43.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When you see it, you'd know right away -\Nit's a marvelous farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:48.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have full control over that farm\Nand would be able to build it according to your vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:51.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But Mr. Princeton, Lucy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:54.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, I can guarantee Lucy's happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:58.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If only you would allow us to adopt Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:04:59.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:00.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,God...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:02.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, we'd never...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:05.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can we make it work, Mr. Popple?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:10.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You give me land and I give you Lucy -\Nis that what you're offering, Mr. Princeton?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:10.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:14.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No-no, that's not how I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:17.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only giving you the land as a sign on my goodwill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.74,0:05:21.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, you don't have\Nto give me the answer right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:24.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please take your time to think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:25.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:26.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we can adopt Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:30.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No. I would never even consider Giving Lucy up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:31.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:32.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is this fine with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:34.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Without a doubt!
Comment: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:35.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.61,0:05:40.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Princeton,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:44.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how hard the life gets,\Nparting with our kids
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,is absolutely unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:49.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,All of our property will be Lucy's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:52.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave, Mr. Princeton.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:56.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, you're just another man\Nwho can only think from the position of wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:01.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy is our beloved daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:04.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we can let someone else adopt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:06.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:14.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Comment: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:18.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:24.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir. I had lots of fun.\NI'd like to ride it again sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:26.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:36.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. and Mrs. Popple, if I was unfortunate enough\Nto anger you with what I said, I beg your forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:39.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't change the fact\Nthat my wife adores Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:42.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, adopting her is the only thing\Nshe can think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:44.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how you both feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:48.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, by the way, you didn't mention\Nany of this to Lucy, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:53.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not. I've met the girls on my way here, so I ordered my coachman to circle them around the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:57.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Then, the carriage hasn't returned yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:01.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That sure was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:02.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:03.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:09.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Princeton, thank you very much.\NWe've circled all around the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:11.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Glad you liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy is still outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:15.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I thought she'd be back already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:19.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little following us everywhere,\Nso she got off the carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:21.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't want Little to exhaust himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:24.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But then... Lucy went home early?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:27.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing her, she probably made a side trip somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:33.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My, so you were right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:48.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Princeton, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:50.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What? You mean for the carriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:53.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy heard everything that happened here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:53.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:58.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me very happy to know\Nthat you came to love me that much. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:02.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:07.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way your father and mother\Nwould willingly part with a child as adorable as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:09.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I should've realized that sooner,\Nif only I gave it a little thought. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:14.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come to play at our place again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:18.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, everyone, this is where I bid my farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:23.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:27.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll still give you a tour through the farm,\Njust wait for a few more days, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:28.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need now, Mr. Princeton.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:29.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:32.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be working on your farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:36.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Long story short, I refuse to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:41.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you're saying so\Nbecause my today's proposal offended you in any way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:43.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If so, I can assure you, that's beside the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:46.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer want to work at your farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.99,0:08:49.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:08.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:12.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the matter?\NThis atmosphere is very weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:44.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:46.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Finally home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:48.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Sylvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:51.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't work out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:52.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:54.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you also offer the land?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:55.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:56.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yet they refused even so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:57.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Mr. Popple still wants the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:03.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he wants it so bad it drives him crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:05.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I shouldn't have brought up the question of land.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:10.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I made it seem as though\NI came to discuss buying Lucy with that land.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:14.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:17.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This would certainly leave a scar on Mr. Popple's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:20.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So you believe you should've\Ntalked about the land some other time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:25.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Because of that, he even revoked\Nhis agreement to work on a farm in Gawler.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:30.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's best if you forget about Lucy now, Sylvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't forget about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:36.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it clearly - that is one unfulfillable wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:52.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! A shooting star!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:58.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So you could become dirty rich, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:02.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,With a bunch of servants\Ntending to your every wish too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:09.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You'd have a gorgeous feast every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:13.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Living like a fabulous princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:15.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that be really awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:19.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you ever tell me that you're becoming\NMr. Princeton's adopted daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:23.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you found yourself in my shoes,\Nwhat would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:26.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well if I were you, it's obvious...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:30.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't wanna be adopted\Nby someone else. Period.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:56.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Autumn came. The long summer vacations were over,\Nso we had to go to school again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:58.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:59.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:02.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Here, here. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:05.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little, behave and sit still\Nuntil I return from school, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:08.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also going to school this time.\NYou understand, Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:12.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Starting with this new school term,\NTob is a first-grader.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:14.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back soon, Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:19.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's time for me to go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:20.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:24.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little, I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:30.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Having refused the job at Mr. Princeton's farm,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:34.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,dad now had to work at construction sites,\Neven though he wasn't used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:37.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mostly laying bricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:38.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:40.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:43.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's because I got a day off tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:45.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Only for tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:47.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I should've taken more?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:51.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, who goes back to work\Non the very next day after her wedding ceremony? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:54.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, John said he's going to work on the next day too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:57.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My, my, what a hardworking couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:12:59.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pick up my wedding gown on my way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.39,0:13:04.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better. If you forget that,\Nwe can't hold a ceremony tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:10.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. My sister Clara was finally getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:15.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.01,0:13:16.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:18.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Will I have to go to work too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:21.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:24.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if Clara leaves to live with John,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:26.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,we'll become a family of five, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:28.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:29.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need money, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:33.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course...\NBut I'm sure we'll manage somehow. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:37.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When Clara becomes John's wife,\Nshe won't be bringing money into our family, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:41.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The whole family is getting scattered away...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:46.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Back when we were leaving England,\Nwe never imagined it'd come to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:51.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get a marvelous plot of land,\Nwhere the whole family would be working. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.38,0:13:53.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have plenty of wheat and vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:56.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And the din from the livestock\Nwould never stop on our farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:14:00.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that was exactly what dad dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:08.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:15.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Imbecile! Don't you know it's dangerous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:16.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:31.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:34.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Clara is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:35.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:37.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:41.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And she's carrying a large box too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:42.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's gotta be a wedding gown!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:44.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:47.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey-hey-hey, I wanna carry it too, sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:50.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa there! Be careful not to drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:53.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And... Heave-ho! Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:54.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:57.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:04.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.62,0:15:06.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That sure is pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:08.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:11.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Clara! Won't you try it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:13.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right! To check if they got your measurements right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:17.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about that.\NI made sure to try it on in the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please, put it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:22.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, you'll Clara putting it on tomorrow anyhow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:23.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna see it today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:26.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big deal, Clara!\NJust put it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:29.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, aren't you a stubborn bunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:32.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, then. It fits me perfectly, you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:34.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Quick! Quick! Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:36.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Clara, are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:39.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put it on in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:44.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, help me in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:46.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:51.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should go look at her wearing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:52.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:54.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Boys can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:55.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.90,0:15:58.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can't means you can't. Only I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:16:00.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're a meanie, sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:02.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob, how is Lucy being mean to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:05.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:07.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:11.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, you came to see\Nthe wedding ceremony tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:13.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right. So where's Clara?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:16.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Changing into her wedding gown.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:17.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? She's gonna change into it soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.96,0:16:19.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's just to see if it fits her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:20.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:24.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, where's mom, then?\NIn the kitchen, I assume?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:24.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:26.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:28.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Welcome back, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:39.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's at the door. Go meet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:40.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:41.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:43.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:49.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Clara sure is taking her time with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:52.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't wearing a wedding gown awfully difficult?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:56.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, perhaps it's that she can't fit into it at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:58.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Clara gained a little weight lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:01.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. How is it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:03.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:05.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's bad that I come now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:08.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we needed to meet\Nto settle things for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:12.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, John, you wouldn't wanna see\Nthe bride in her wedding gown today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:15.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I wouldn't mind seeing her, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:19.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I heard that it only okay for you\Nto see the bride after the ceremony had begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:22.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As for seeing her the day before - I'm not so sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:25.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose. Yeah, you're probably right.\NI don't wanna see her today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:30.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, go tell Clara\Nthat she can't leave her room just yet. Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:33.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Plus, I'll get to look at her myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:35.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna look too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:41.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Guess I can call you "brother," starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:43.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I can too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I... I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:48.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that'll make sense. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:52.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No... I feel a little embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:55.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:04.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So pretty, sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:05.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty, alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:06.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:09.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, I never forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:13.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You also contributed your five shillings\Ninto this wedding gown.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:14.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:16.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say my thanks once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.98,0:18:18.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:35.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,On the next day, Clara and John got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:37.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Those two looked very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:54.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The reception party was held in our very own backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:18:59.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,With foods and drinks and dances,\Nit became very lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:07.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,John's little brother Paul.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The bride looks gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:11.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Mac and Mr. Bernard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:13.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Mr. Popple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:14.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.31,0:19:17.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Jamling and Mr. Parker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:18.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.16,0:19:20.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As well as Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:22.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And some of John's colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:27.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Our backyard became crowded\Nwith folk from the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:57.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When the guests left,\NBen returned to the port,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:20:00.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,and John went home together with Clara,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:03.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,our house has suddenly become very lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.09,0:20:08.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And dad just kept drinking in silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:17.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Both me and Lucy were thoroughly worn out\Nand didn't even have the energy to speak out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:20.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So our house became quieter than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:31.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:35.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then it started raining outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:04.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's wrong, you hear me?! Lucy-May Popple,\Nbe more attentive. And now, redo it once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:07.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The egg came first, I'm tellin' ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:09.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I know it was the chicken!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:37.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be nice if dad got some land\Nwhere the whole family could work together?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:38.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:40.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it'll ever happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:44.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You think it will, Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:50.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look like it. So far,\Nthings have only been changing from bad to worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:56.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,From bad to worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:21.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.79,0:22:23.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You go ahead without me, Tob.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.10,0:22:25.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.49,0:22:27.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I need to stop by at one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:33.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What about the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.86,0:22:36.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the teacher I'm taking a day off!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.33,0:23:13.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you here, Lucy.\NAre you having this whole day to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:13.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.70,0:23:16.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's just great.\NMy wife would be happy to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.29,0:23:20.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone at home doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:22.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Princeton.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.51,0:23:23.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
